title: lifelines
description:
“lifelines” is an original artwork by artist Galina Lugonja

Size: 50 x 70 cm
Edition: Original piece, signed by the artist (1 edition only)
Technique: D.G.A; Analogue drawing digitalized and digitally processed. Printed with the gicléer method on 0,5 mm fine art quality hemp paper in Grünerløkka, Oslo.
Artist thoughts: 〰️ Lifelines 〰️ I often wonder how destined our lives are. I do believe there is a larger than life energy supporting our soul development here on Earth. Maybe it isn’t as black/white as either being destined or coincidental. Probably more complex than I’ll ever grasp. This is where I let go
